title: Syria-Kurd pact could add to fog of war
text:
Syria-Kurd pact could add to fog of war 10:03am EST - 01:28 
Militias allied to the Syrian government will enter the Afrin region within hours, state media reported on Monday, after a reported deal to help Kurdish forces repel a Turkish assault. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
